problems.instructions:
CUDA kernels run on the GPU and must be marked with the __global__ keyword.

Syntax:
__global__ void kernelName() {
    // GPU code
}

In this problem:
1. Define a kernel named helloKernel
2. Inside the kernel, print exactly:
   Hello from GPU kernel!

Note: You are only defining the kernel. Do NOT launch it yet.

