problems.instructions:
CUDA provides dim3 to define grid and block dimensions.

Syntax:
dim3 blocks(2);
dim3 threads(4);

kernel<<<blocks, threads>>>();

Rewrite a kernel launch using dim3 instead of raw integers.

The kernel should print global thread ID for 2 blocks and 4 threads.

